00:00:50.468 --> 00:00:51.557
on what would be helpful.

00:00:52.114 --> 00:00:53.310
One of the things you
learn when you

00:00:53.327 --> 00:00:54.564
start to think about mentoring

00:00:54.612 --> 00:00:57.370
