00:03:48.182 --> 00:03:49.513
very few women at the university.

00:03:49.879 --> 00:03:52.166
Pat Graham was my dean

00:03:52.238 --> 00:03:54.529
and she was the first woman dean
at the university,

00:03:54.732 --> 00:03:56.716
