and so we actually are hiring quite a fewó

00:09:18.579 --> 00:09:22.776
by that I mean,
we have only 70 FTE facultyó

00:09:23.056 --> 00:09:27.796
and weíre hiring in
proportion to that,

00:09:28.363 --> 00:09:30.116
quite a few people.

